OL,3,CMore than 1,000 victims protected
OL,4,Cunder domestic abuse order pilot scheme
OL,6,FMore than a thousand victims across
OL,7,Fthe UK have been protected through
OL,8,Ftougher restrictions on domestic
OL,9,Fabusers piloted over the last year.
OL,11,FDomestic Abuse Protection Orders have
OL,12,Fbeen trialed by forces, including the
OL,13,FMetropolitan Police, since November
OL,14,Flast year ahead of a planned national
OL,15,Frollout.
