OL,3,CMore than 1,000 victims protected
OL,4,Cunder domestic abuse order pilot scheme
OL,6,FUnder the orders, courts can set
OL,7,Fconditions for as long as needed to
OL,8,Fprotect victims of all forms of
OL,9,Fdomestic abuse, including economic,
OL,10,Fcoercive behaviour, stalking and
OL,11,F"honour"-based violence.
OL,13,FSince last year, officers in Croydon,
OL,14,FBromley and Sutton issued 219
OL,15,Femergency notices and secured 180
OL,16,Fcourt-backed Domestic Abuse Protection
OL,17,FOrders (DAPOs), orders which can stop
OL,18,Fabusers from contacting victims,
OL,19,Fturning up at their homes, or posting
OL,20,Fharmful content online.
