OL,3,CMore than 1,000 victims protected
OL,4,Cunder domestic abuse order pilot scheme
OL,6,F"The 180 Domestic Abuse Protection
OL,7,FOrders issued and enforced within the
OL,8,Fpilot are helping to prevent repeat
OL,9,Fvictims.
OL,11,F"The orders are another tool to
OL,12,Fprotect victims, alongside driving up
OL,13,Fcharges for serious offences including
OL,14,Frape and serious sexual assault and
OL,15,Fproviding additional training to
OL,16,Fofficers."
