OL,3,CMore than 1,000 victims protected
OL,4,Cunder domestic abuse order pilot scheme
OL,6,F"But with more than 1,000 Domestic
OL,7,FAbuse Protection Orders issued across
OL,8,FEngland and Wales, we are taking real,
OL,9,Fpractical steps to protect victims
OL,10,Fthat really do make a difference.
OL,12,FVictims minister Alex Davies-Jones
OL,13,Fadded: "These protection orders are
OL,14,Fthe first and strongest of their kind.
OL,15,FVictims need more than promises ` they
OL,16,Fneed real action."
