OL,3,CMore than 1,000 victims protected
OL,4,Cunder domestic abuse order pilot scheme
OL,6,FThe orders have currently been
OL,7,Flaunched in Greater Manchester, London
OL,8,Fboroughs of Croydon, Bromley and
OL,9,FSutton, Cleveland, North Wales and
OL,10,Falso used by British Transport Police.
OL,12,FThe announcement comes as ministers
OL,13,Fhave vowed to halve violence against
OL,14,Fwomen and girls in the next 10 years
OL,15,Fbut have yet to publish its strategy
OL,16,Fto do so.
