OL,6,FIn September, domestic abuse
OL,7,Fcommissioner Dame Nicole Jacobs said
OL,8,Fshe cannot see momentum within the
OL,9,FGovernment to fulfil its pledge and
OL,10,Fcriticised the delay over the
OL,11,Fstrategy's publication, warning
OL,12,Fvictims "cannot wait any longer".
